00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:04,860
Company...halt!

459
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:11,990
- Who wants what? It's all free.
- Arsenal!

460
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:14,300
- Shut up!
- Up yours!

461
00:41:14,470 --> 00:41:17,310
- I want a woman!
- You want a woman.

462
00:41:17,470 --> 00:41:19,940
- Yeah!
